^^^^^^^

.. figure:: https://github.com/emptyxl/coder/raw/master/example_images/unicode.png
   :alt: Unicode


Hex to Dec
^^^^^^^^^^

It only supports the transformation between numeric, more than one
numeric interval by space \` \`

